{
  "stem": "25423.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I lived with people who were decent, who tried to live by the gospels-- I didn't say that they were perfect-- who provided me with shelter and never made me feel that I'm an outsider, who accepted the same risk of being caught and shot, which faced me by the simple fact that I'm there.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And while there was a storm all around me, I was, in a way, like in a Noah's arc.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Were you aware that there were other Jews there?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Slowly and gradually, because this was a silent order.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we communicated only half an hour a day in the circle of recreation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then gradually, they let me know indirectly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Monks.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, just hinted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One saw my brother somewhere, and he is well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Another mentioned that the Jew is sitting in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A third one told me that this German priest, Father Peters, keeps four Jewish families-- [LAUGHS] --In the cellar of the factory which he run, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all of this was-- and one day I met a monk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was Brother Daniel with a beard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I asked him-- he didn't know that I'm Jewish because I already looked-- he was not in the same monastery as I was.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I asked him, Father Daniel, what are you doing?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, he says, I'm, I'm running a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had-- he ran an orphanage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in this orphanage, there were three Ukrainian children and 17 Jewish children, boys.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, every Ukrainian knows what the [NON-ENGLISH] is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They lived together, you see, for centuries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I've never encountered any homosexuality.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "None.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's only a figment of the imagination of the sick, Western mind, especially American mind.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
